***Express generator***

1. hum logo ko kaafi saara kaam karna padta hai express
setup krne mein iska matlab har baar jab hum naya
project banaayege to har baar fir se utna hi kaam krna
padega, matlab ki poora code likho and sab kuchh setup
karo, is time ko bacha sakte ho with help of express
generator, use express generator and it will make the
folder structure for you and it will also write the
basic code for the project.
**installation**
steps:-* npm i express-generator -g
steps:-* express lolopopo --view=ejs
**two changes**
1 app.get -> router.get  
2 npx nodemon filename -> npx nodemon



***MongoDB***

har naye app ka data store hoga storage mein, par usey directly rakne
ki jagah ek container mein rakhege, us container mein sirf us app ka
data aayega

 Model(code) => collection (db)
 schema (code) => documents (db) 

1. ek app ka poora data => database.

2. ek app mein variety of data hota hai par poora data hota app ka hi
   hai, par us data ka sub category kehlaata hai "collection".

3. collection matlab ki bola users ka data, ek user pe baat kri to hua
   "document".



